  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 375°F.",
    "Heat olive oil in a large oven‑proof skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add diced onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Stir in minced garlic, sliced mushrooms, diced carrots, smoked paprika, and oregano; cook for 5 minutes.",
    "Add sliced red peppers, tomato paste, balsamic vinegar, salt and pepper, and stir to coat.",
    "Transfer skillet to the oven and bake for 20 minutes, stirring once.",
    "Remove from oven and pour the glaze over the vegetables.",
    "Sprinkle grated cheddar cheese evenly over the casserole.",
    "Return to oven and bake for another 5 minutes until cheese is melted.",
    "Let rest for 5 minutes, then serve hot."
  ],
